      <div class="content">
        <div class="emailFilter"><p>He mentioned Trisquel :D<br />
It's when reading the interviews of RMS that I realise his genius. Look at<br />
how he answers, how everything he says clarifies things. Instantly ethical<br />
issues are separated from technical and legal ones, everything complicated is<br />
quickly analysed and explained in a simple way. He isn't afraid to tell you<br />
when he does an educated guess and when he just doesn't want to answer all<br />
together, which is something I've rarely ever seen happen with philosophers,<br />
especially the second. Everything this man has to say about software is gold.</p>
