      <div class="content">
        <div class="emailFilter"><p>Software as a service is "pretty much the same thing" as local software from the technical point of view but absolutely not from the point of view of the control the user has on her computation. That is the only point the FSF cares about! She has no way to access the code. She does not even have access to a binary! How can she make sure that the service is only doing what she wants and not anything malicious? How can she modify the service to make it do what she needs (for instance correcting a bug)?</p>
